==At the boat==
===Talking to Anne or Will===
* '''Will:''' Lovely! The open sea!
* '''Player:''' It's not really that open... We haven't even left port yet.
* '''Anne:''' Well, good news, [player name], because that's where you come in! You're our new helm!
* '''Player:''' Helm?
* '''Will:''' It means you're in charge of the ship's helm! In other words, you're responsible for steering the ship!
* '''Player:''' It's more of a boat really...
* '''Anne:''' Well, we all have to start somewhere!
* '''Player:''' Right... So if I'm manning the helm, what will you two be doing?
* '''Will:''' Well, it's simple, isn't it? We're in charge!
* '''Player:''' Have you ever actually done this before?
* '''Anne:''' Many times!
* '''Will:''' Just never on our own ship before! This is an exciting first day for... well, we haven't actually named our business yet, but I'm sure we'll come up with a good name soon.
* '''Player:''' And what does this business do?
* '''Anne:''' We salvage shipwrecks of course!
* '''Player:''' Of course. Alright then, I don't remember doing it, but apparently I committed to this. Where is our first wreck?
* '''Will:''' We've got a good one to get us started! Last time we were on the Pandemonium, we purchased a map that should lead us to an old pirate wreck.
* '''Player:''' The Pandemonium?
* '''Anne:''' Have you never been? It's a great place for a drink! We'll have to take you there!
* '''Will:''' But first, let's collect some salvage! According to the map, the wreck is just east of the Karamja Shipyard, so south of here.
* '''Anne:''' Over to you, [player name]! Take the helm when ready.
* {{tact|end}}

