==At the Pandemonium==
===Talking to 'Squawking' Steve Beanie===
* ''''Squawking' Steve Beanie:''' Yo ho ho and a Jolly Roger to you, me hearty! I can see from the fact that you're totally drenched from head to toe that you are a fellow scallywag sailor! The name's Steve Beanie! Pleased to meet you.
* '''Player:''' I think I must be having some sort of fever dream... or maybe I'm dead?
* ''''Squawking' Steve Beanie:''' Ha! Far from it, matey! Though the fever dream I can't comment on. They're rather common around here... but I assure you that it's well-nigh certainly like enough most likely not the rum doing it!
* '''Player:''' Okay... You said words there, but I don't think they actually formed a sentence.
* ''''Squawking' Steve Beanie:''' Ah, me wee hearty! You seem to be having quite the crisis! Thankfully, you've rigged the starboard and docked yourself at the right port! Welcome to the Pandemonium!
* '''Player:''' Pandemonium?
* ''''Squawking' Steve Beanie:''' Aye! To be sure! This here is the finest establishment in all the seas. Sit back! Have a drink! Let the good times, and the rum, flow!
* '''Player:''' If this is the Pandemonium, do you know of a pair of salvagers called Will and Anne?
* ''''Squawking' Steve Beanie:''' Avast ye! You name a pair of pinching looting plundering seadogs!
* '''Player:''' I see. So you do know them. They claimed to have purchased a map here, but I'm guessing they weren't being totally honest about that...
* ''''Squawking' Steve Beanie:''' Purchased?! Purchased?! You're pulling my leg, you scallywag! Those scurvy dogs came here and broke the one rule of the Pandemonium! That map was pilfered! Stolen!
* '''Player:''' Well, I had quite the fun run in with them myself. They had me help them salvage an old shipwreck before throwing me overboard.
* ''''Squawking' Steve Beanie:''' Arrr, you poor scallywag.
* '''Player:''' Thank you. It was the map they stole that led them to the wreck. What do you know about it?
* ''''Squawking' Steve Beanie:''' Not a lot, I'm afraid. You should hoist your sails and go speak to Ribs instead. It was his map they looted. He's the old dog over in the corner. Avast!
* {{tact|end}}

